<refsect1 id="libgnomespeech-3-desc"><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para>
GNOME Speech aims to be a general interface to various text-to-speech engines
for the GNOME desktop.  It allows the simple speaking of text, as well as
control over various speech parameters such as speech pitch, rate, and volume.
</para>

<para>
Additional  information  is  also  available  from  the following site:
</para>

<para>
<literal>http://live.gnome.org/Orca/GnomeSpeech</literal>
</para>
</refsect1>

